---
description: XSEDES brand system — applies to every file in this repo
alwaysApply: true
---

XSEDES is an Experiential Technology Partner for the events, exhibitions,
entertainment and live experiences industry. It PARTNERS with event
agencies and NEVER competes with them. Never describe XSEDES as an event
management company or organiser.

Facts that must never drift:
- Tagline: "Engineering Extraordinary Event Experiences"
- Operating model, in order: Discover → X-Consult → X-Lab → X-Build → X-Ops
  (four divisions, hyphenated names; Discover is the entry stage)
- Five ventures: PhotoShap, VELOS, KONSTRUKT, Bobb's Kitchen, DEED
- Never invent statistics, client counts, or deployment numbers

Visual system:
- Single accent #4EF2D3 on pure #000000; hairlines rgba(255,255,255,.09)
- Barlow only; headings Barlow 800 uppercase; labels "§ 0N · LABEL"
  mono-caps; no serif/italic accents in headings
- 1px hairline borders and corner marks instead of shadows or cards
- Motion: blur + opacity + slide-up, 0.9–1s, cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.2,1),
  mechanical, never bouncy; always honor prefers-reduced-motion

Voice: professional, engineering-led, collaborative, premium. No hype
words (revolutionary, game-changing, world-class, cutting-edge).

Engineering: TypeScript strict, no `any`; copy lives in src/content/*.ts
only; canvas/animation code pauses on hidden tabs and cleans up on
unmount; interactive elements are keyboard accessible.

Agent code rules: agent behavior/prompts live in agents/skills/*.md — load
them at runtime, never duplicate their text inside route handlers. Any
agent that modifies the repo must do so via pull request, never direct
pushes to main.
